Now, our queen,
she made her peace with change.

11:20.806 --> 11:22.183
She told herself

11:22.350 --> 11:24.810
the back seat's
got cushions too.

11:24.977 --> 11:26.562
She told herself

11:26.729 --> 11:28.981
she was playing the game

11:29.148 --> 11:31.484
by staying in it.

11:33.486 --> 11:35.571
Excuse me.

11:37.239 --> 11:38.616
Do you know
where the bathroom is?

11:38.783 --> 11:40.618
There's one in the back.

11:41.660 --> 11:43.829
I don't see it.

11:46.248 --> 11:48.667
Show me.

12:34.839 --> 12:36.382
Where did 30F run off to?

12:36.549 --> 12:39.218
