as I'm still alive...

12:40.261 --> 12:41.637
..I can adapt.

12:41.804 --> 12:43.472
So you can
let everyone back home

12:43.639 --> 12:45.057
know where you're going.

12:45.224 --> 12:48.519
I still know what I am.

13:24.889 --> 13:26.265
But America too

13:26.432 --> 13:28.934
can take issue
with a woman of power.

13:29.101 --> 13:32.563
It finds ways
of cutting her down,

13:32.730 --> 13:36.317
of punishing her
for her daring to be.

14:31.622 --> 14:33.415
And our girl...

14:34.875 --> 14:38.504
..after a while, even she forgot
there's a queen inside.

14:59.942 --> 15:02.278
<i>ISIS fighters
destroyed the ancient temple,</i>

15:02.444 --> 15:04.196
<i>a once popular
tourist attraction</i>

15:04.363 --> 15:06.490
<i>recently denounced
by ISIS militants</i>

15:06.657 --> 15:09.868
<i>as "the necessary destruction
of idolatrous structures</i>

15:10.035 --> 15:12.621
<i>"in accordance
with Islamic law."</i>

15:12.788 --> 15:14.707
And there's no end

15:14.873 --> 15:19.044
to the cruelty of men
threatened by strong women.

15:24.174 --> 15:26.552
So what's a queen to do?

15:28.262 --> 15:30.806
She gets on her knees.

15:30.973 --> 15:35.019
She takes
what she don't want to

15:35.185 --> 15:38.147
and we watch
in easy fucking judgement

15:38.314 --> 15:42.693
and pretend we'd do a single thing
different in her shoes.

15:56.457 --> 15:58.000
Hm.

15:59.043 --> 16:01.086
I hear they blew up your altar.

16:03.631 --> 16:05.174
Darn.

16:05.341 --> 16:08.969
I have a new one to offer you.

16:11.722 --> 16:13.766
Aren't you the lucky duck?

16:19.188 --> 16:21.231
Oh!

16:21.398 --> 16:23.025
Boop.

16:23.192 --> 16:25.069
OK.

16:32.785 --> 16:36.038
Worship
is a volume business.

16:37.456 --> 16:42.586
Whosoever has the most followers
wins the game.

16:51.136 --> 16:53.097
Want to play?

16:55.224 --> 16:58.602
Life is long
when you got regret.

16:59.895 --> 17:03.982
A moment can last forever

17:04.149 --> 17:06.985
when you can see
how it should have gone.

17:08.654 --> 17:11.240
You get the moral to this story?

17:11.407 --> 17:13.283
I don't know.

17:13.450 --> 17:15.035
Don't compromise?

17:15.202 --> 17:16.578
Or, uh...

17:16.745 --> 17:18.497
..don't cut deals
with treacherous motherfuckers.

17:18.664 --> 17:20.541
What? No!

17:20.708 --> 17:22.167
Fuck, no!

17:22.334 --> 17:24.211
Did you get this one
off the discount rack?

17:24.378 --> 17:26.422
Where are you getting in life

17:26.588 --> 17:28.257
without some fucking compromise?

17:28.424 --> 17:29.675
The moral is...

17:29.842 --> 17:31.218
Get myself a queen.

17:31.385 --> 17:32.845
You goddamn right.

17:33.011 --> 17:35.472
You better get yourself a queen.

17:35.639 --> 17:38.392
'Cause you just went and killed
one of theirs.

17:38.559 --> 17:41.603
That's one of mine.
I killed one of mine.

17:41.770 --> 17:43.397
Not anymore.

17:43.564 --> 17:47.526
Not in a LONG while
has he been one of yours.

17:47.693 --> 17:49.903
You separate a head from a body,

17:50.070 --> 17:53.907
that is strike fucking one
across the bow.

17:54.074 --> 17:55.826
They ain't gonna
take that lightly.

17:55.993 --> 17:58.036
Good - wait till
he sees strike two,

17:58.203 --> 18:00.581
when I get myself that queen.

18:07.004 --> 18:08.714
What about you?

18:08.881 --> 18:11.759
Spill blood together,
that binds you to him for life.

18:11.925 --> 18:14.595
- Yeah, the fuck it does.
- Fuck it doesn't.

18:14.762 --> 18:17.598
- Now, we have a compact.
- Yeah. Till you piss me off.

18:17.765 --> 18:19.475
You've just gone
and pissed me off, OK?

18:19.641 --> 18:21.101
So I think that violates
our agreement.

18:21.268 --> 18:22.811
