did you think he was?

18:33.030 --> 18:34.406
You're getting one too.

18:34.573 --> 18:36.950
We have to be presentable,
where we're going.

18:37.117 --> 18:38.494
Fuck you!

18:38.660 --> 18:40.370
Look, I don't even
know your name!

18:40.537 --> 18:42.664
Hey, Mr Wednesday?
Who I met on a Wednesday.

18:42.831 --> 18:45.834
