I'm aware.

18:53.509 --> 18:54.968
You're confused.

18:55.135 --> 18:57.304
You got questions,
but you don't know how to ask them.

18:57.471 --> 19:00.557
Do not confuse confusion
for anger.

19:01.725 --> 19:03.936
I'm not confused.

19:06.355 --> 19:08.982
I'm VERY confused.

19:09.149 --> 19:11.151
You're confused.
And you're intrigued.

19:11.318 --> 19:13.904
Your wife came back from the dead.
Why wouldn't you be?

19:14.071 --> 19:15.823
If you denied it,
I'd call you a liar.

19:15.989 --> 19:17.825
- A bigger one than I am.
- Ha!

19:17.991 --> 19:20.244
And that's a very big liar.

19:20.410 --> 19:21.370
Hm...

19:21.537 --> 19:24.540
The terms of our agreement
are intact.

19:24.706 --> 19:27.167
You're not angry, Shadow.

19:27.334 --> 19:29.962
But you do have to start
getting angry.

19:30.128 --> 19:33.507
Angry...gets shit done.

19:34.550 --> 19:36.343
Try that on for size.

20:57.341 --> 20:58.717
Is this Wisconsin?

20:58.884 --> 21:00.677
That's our NEXT stop.

21:00.844 --> 21:03.472
Welcome to Kentucky.

21:15.150 --> 21:18.403
Now, be nice to the lady we're visiting,
but not too nice.

21:18.570 --> 21:21.531
She might take a fancy to you
and that would not be good.

21:21.698 --> 21:25.410
Why? She an ex-girlfriend
of yours?

21:26.453 --> 21:29.164
Not for all the little plastic toys
in China.

21:29.331 --> 21:31.166
No, she's...

21:32.542 --> 21:34.419
She's something else.

21:50.102 --> 21:53.605
We might not be welcome
at first.

22:33.270 --> 22:37.816
Ah...in the presence of a queen.

23:00.464 --> 23:02.090
Huh. Forgot it was Easter.

23:02.257 --> 23:05.969
Well, it is Sunday,
16th of April,

23:06.136 --> 23:08.638
seven days
after the vernal equinox.

23:11.099 --> 23:14.227
- I love Easter.
- Oh, many do.

23:15.270 --> 23:18.398
Some for the rabbits,
some for the resurrection.

23:18.565 --> 23:21.193
Most think of the food.

23:21.359 --> 23:23.904
All that fucking sugar, huh?

23:24.071 --> 23:26.656
They don't think
of the truth of the day.

23:26.823 --> 23:29.910
And why would they?

23:31.787 --> 23:33.705
But, yeah, you could...

23:33.872 --> 23:36.541
..you could call this Easter.

23:36.708 --> 23:38.418
Or we could call it
what it really is.

23:38.585 --> 23:41.588
A pagan ritual, the celebration
of the beginning of spring,

23:41.755 --> 23:44.174
dating back about 12,000 years.

23:44.341 --> 23:46.843
So when you see children
dipping eggs

23:47.010 --> 23:49.137
in vinegar the colours
of their favourite toys,

23:49.304 --> 23:53.016
when you see the nation's youth
fleeing south for copulation,

23:53.183 --> 23:55.102
or when they spread their seed

23:55.268 --> 23:58.021
over that sinking mass
that is the great state of Florida,

23:58.188 --> 23:59.773
they all...

23:59.940 --> 24:01.650
..without realising it,

24:01.817 --> 24:04.444
do it in her name.

24:06.029 --> 24:07.572
Ostara.

24:11.785 --> 24:13.745
Hello!

24:16.581 --> 24:19.417
Oh, it is a treasure and a treat

24:19.584 --> 24:21.795
to welcome you all to my home

24:21.962 --> 24:25.132
and on my day,
my favourite day of the year.

24:25.298 --> 24:28.260
When all is lavender and dew,

24:28.426 --> 24:30.345
reborn and restored.

24:30.512 --> 24:32.264
- When we celebrate...
- Hello, Shadow.

24:34.975 --> 24:36.518
Hey.

24:37.561 --> 24:38.979
Do I know you?

24:39.146 --> 24:41.648
Yes, you do.

24:43.108 --> 24:45.944
..and then move on.

24:46.111 --> 24:48.738
I think it's important
for us all to remember

24:48.905 --> 24:52.409
what this day is
really, truly about, which is...

24:52.576 --> 24:55.537
Ooh, for Christ's sake.

24:58.373 --> 24:59.749
Praise the Lords.

24:59.916 --> 25:02.711
Please help yourself
and those less fortunate to the buffet.

25:02.878 --> 25:04.963
I got plenty of honey ham.

25:05.130 --> 25:07.382
But for those of you
who do not partake of pork...

25:07.549 --> 25:09.509
That's...

25:10.635 --> 25:12.721
..Easter?

25:12.888 --> 25:14.639
Because people
believe in Easter.

25:14.806 --> 25:18.226
Believing is seeing.

25:18.393 --> 25:20.562
Gods are real
if you believe in them.

25:41.249 --> 25:43.543
Gods.

25:43.710 --> 25:45.128
Uh-huh.

25:45.295 --> 25:47.047
Fuck me.

25:47.214 --> 25:49.549
- Alright, so...
- Hm?

25:49.716 --> 25:51.676
That's...Jesus Christ.

25:51.843 --> 25:53.220
A Jesus Christ.

25:53.386 --> 25:56.139
Some Jesus Christ.

25:56.306 --> 25:59.184
For every belief, every branch,
every denomination,

25:59.351 --> 26:02.270
they see a different face
when they close their eyes to pray.

26:02.437 --> 26:04.481
So who are you?

26:04.648 --> 26:08.735
Like I said, you wouldn't
believe in me if I told you.

26:11.905 --> 26:14.324
Happy Easter, you old fraud.

26:14.491 --> 26:17.369
And a fair Ostara to you.

26:17.535 --> 26:19.412
What the hell
are you doing here?

26:19.579 --> 26:21.623
I'm not here for Christ's sake,
but all our sakes.

26:21.790 --> 26:23.166
You look divine.

26:23.333 --> 26:24.876
How the hell else should I look?

26:25.043 --> 26:28.213
Say hello to Ostara.

26:30.674 --> 26:32.759
Hey, Ostara.

26:33.802 --> 26:36.054
Oh, he's a blusher.

26:36.221 --> 26:37.430
- Wednesday.
- Mm-hm?

26:37.597 --> 26:39.099
- You brought me a blusher.
- Mm-hm.

26:39.266 --> 26:42.560
And he's pink chocolate.
How perfectly wonderful.

26:42.727 --> 26:44.771
What's he called?

26:44.938 --> 26:47.065
Shadow Moon.

26:57.409 --> 26:59.619
So, how's tricks?

26:59.786 --> 27:02.747
Asks the tricksiest rabbit
I know.

27:02.914 --> 27:06.251
Well, I was hoping
to enlist your assistance.

27:06.418 --> 27:08.336
Stop wasting time.

27:08.503 --> 27:11.131
I can't be bothered,
so don't you bother me about it.

27:11.298 --> 27:13.842
Shadow? That's a sweet name.

27:14.009 --> 27:16.720
Now, now, now, now.
Leave him be, huh?

27:16.886 --> 27:18.847
Why do they call you Shadow,
sweetness?

27:19.014 --> 27:20.807
The way I followed my mama
around.

27:20.974 --> 27:23.852
She didn't know
what else to call me.

27:24.019 --> 27:25.854
Well, I deal in sugar, Sugar,

27:26.021 --> 27:28.315
and you're the sweetest damn thing
I've ever seen.

27:30.025 --> 27:32.360
This is the boy
that has everyone so upset?

27:32.527 --> 27:34.237
Ah, you heard?

27:34.404 --> 27:36.740
Well, I keep my ears pricked up.

27:36.906 --> 27:38.366
Come here, sweet Shadow.

27:38.533 --> 27:40.410
Allow me to impart some wisdom.

27:40.577 --> 27:42.912
There's far too many
secret societies out there.

27:43.079 --> 27:45.582
They have no loyalty
and no love.

27:45.749 --> 27:48.918
They range from barely competent
to deeply dangerous.

27:49.085 --> 27:51.421
- You don't sound like one of us.
- I'm not one of you.

27:51.588 --> 27:52.964
Oh, yes, you are.

27:53.131 --> 27:56.634
You're as forgotten, unloved
and unremembered as any of us.

27:56.801 --> 27:58.303
I'm doing just fine.

27:58.470 --> 28:01.431
Happy Easter. Christ is risen.
Hello, boys.

28:01.598 --> 28:03.183
Well, you were
before these assholes were born.

28:03.350 --> 28:05.727
Until the day that Jesus Christ

28:05.894 --> 28:08.355
crawled out
of his stinky old grave,

28:08.521 --> 28:12.901
