on eggs and rabbit and candy.

28:25.413 --> 28:27.832
- And they do it in my name.
- Serious question, my dear.

28:27.999 --> 28:30.710
I have no doubt that millions
upon millions exchange tokens

28:30.877 --> 28:32.462
and observe the rituals
of your festival,

28:32.629 --> 28:34.381
all down to the hunting
of the hidden eggs,

28:34.547 --> 28:37.384
but does anybody pray
in your name?

28:38.426 --> 28:40.345
Do they say it in worship?

28:40.512 --> 28:41.971
Oh, they mouth your name,

28:42.138 --> 28:44.808
mm, but they have no idea
what it means, none whatsoever.

28:44.974 --> 28:48.061
Same every spring - you do
all the work, he gets the prayers.

28:48.228 --> 28:50.021
What has gotten into you?

28:50.188 --> 28:52.273
I feel terrible about this.

28:52.440 --> 28:53.858
No. No!

28:54.025 --> 28:56.444
It's her day.
You took it.

28:56.611 --> 28:58.196
You crucified her day.

28:58.363 --> 29:00.365
