everybody else got burned.

29:00.532 --> 29:01.908
In YOUR name.

29:02.075 --> 29:04.160
Happy fucking Easter!

29:04.327 --> 29:06.663
Uh...

29:06.830 --> 29:09.082
N...

29:11.167 --> 29:13.420
- A word.
- Mm-hm.

29:22.303 --> 29:25.557
You shut your mouth before
I slap it off your goddamn face!

29:25.723 --> 29:28.351
Oh... Oh. How dare you?

29:28.518 --> 29:29.936
How dare you?

29:30.103 --> 29:32.188
How dare you come into my home

29:32.355 --> 29:34.232
and uncork
all over Jesus of Nazareth

29:34.399 --> 29:36.860
and all the other Jesuses
who died on the cross

29:37.026 --> 29:39.320
and even the ones who didn't -
how dare you!

29:39.487 --> 29:41.030
These are kind, generous men

29:41.197 --> 29:42.782
and they've come to celebrate
their day.

29:42.949 --> 29:44.325
My day.

29:44.492 --> 29:46.286
God damn it, OUR day!

29:46.453 --> 29:48.830
And you come in here
and disrespect them?

29:48.997 --> 29:51.541
- They are gods, for God's sake!
- They're sons of.

